    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior retains a strong shine, though there are a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only slight wear on the driver\u2019s seat bolster and steering wheel. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. It is a solid, honest example of this model that is ready to be driven and enjoyed immediately.",
